Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:10.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I can't stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.53,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brain Hazard{\i0} airs soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:21.68,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,No, no anime breaks. \NI know I won't return to studying after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:23.54,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Exams start tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Welp, it's on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:40.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wow, I've become such a scatterbrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:47.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I've forgotten how to put in the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:53.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Plug away, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:57.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Gotta at least make sure \Nmy rep doesn't affect Alya's standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:01.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh?
