Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.97,italicstop,ALYA,0,0,0,,Good evening, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.28,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, hey there. Something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.30,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I didn't call for a specific \Nreason or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.69,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What's up? Did you miss me that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:55.98,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What was that thud?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.86,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nothing. So, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:06.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Well, you said you're prone \Nto slacking when you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.12,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if you were \Nstudying like you're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.98,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if you were \Nstudying like you're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nope. I can't stay motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:17.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'd like to know how you \Nkeep it up at times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.76,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,"Keep it up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:22.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No idea. I don't lose\Nmotivation to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.39,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously? That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.22,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,If you're having trouble staying focused,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.09,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,why don't we make a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:29.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.96,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What's your goal for these exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.68,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'd like to place in the top 30 for our year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.86,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Aiming big, are we? Well, that works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,If you manage to hit that goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.91,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll do one thing you ask for—anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hm? {\i1}Anything,{\i0} you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.91,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Within reason, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.83,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.77,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What if I don't hit the goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.00,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You'll do one thing I ask for, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.45,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Kinda does things for me, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:59.42,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:04.59,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, I wasn't implying I wanted to be \Nordered around in a masochistic way or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:06.51,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Given name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.26,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I just gave you a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.69,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not much of a hint when you say it in Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.64,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Heh, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.65,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Anyway, do we have a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.25,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make you regret offering that bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.77,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd love to see you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.73,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You've gotten better at ignoring my outbursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.73,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You're making big bro cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.60,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Since when have you been my big bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,We're the same age!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:37.92,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't your birthday November 7th?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:41.80,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,It is... How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I think you mentioned it in your \Nclass introduction when you transferred in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.28,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,My birthday is April 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.56,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I've already turned sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I've already turned sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.79,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Anyway, thanks for checking in, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:00.89,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.52,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:09.14,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I can't believe she realized I'd lost focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.91,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Are our minds linked or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:16.67,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I called because \NI got spooked by a horror show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.86,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No chance I was telling him that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.64,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But what the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Why didn't he tell me his birthday? \NI would've celebrated it with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Didn't he say we were friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.98,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun, you jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.68,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1.5\fs25\pos(320,86.727)\c&HFDF8FA&}Five Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Finally done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:41.09,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Good job powering through exams, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.02,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:52.33,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fnComic Sans MS\fs23\c&HC4D5C0&\an8\frx4\fry350\frz9.997\pos(522.909,72.909)}3. Modern Lit.\N\N\N\N\NLunch Break\N\N\N\N\N\NIntro Chem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:48.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, do you have any plans after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No, not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wanna walk partway home together, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'd like to discuss what we're doing \Nfor the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.33,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.35,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:06.10,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She hasn't flirted with me in Russian \Nonce since that phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.98,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,So, you wanted to talk about \Nthe closing ceremony speeches?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:12.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah... but first,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:16.89,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,haven't you been acting kinda \Ndifferent since the exam period started?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.46,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I thought I'd made sure it didn't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It pretty much didn't, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But I could just tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:32.12,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,R-Really? So you cared enough \Nto pay that much attention to me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.60,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Even during exam period?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:38.00,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Of course I care. You're my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.91,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.82,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.54,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Your birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.26,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:53.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Why didn't you invite me \Nto your birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,My birthday what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I didn't have a party. Who told you I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.08,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You didn't have one? \NYou expect me to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:01.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.95,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,O-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:08.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Is it commonplace for people to have \Nbirthday parties in Russia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.28,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.19,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Is it not in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:16.05,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Dunno about everyone else, \Nbut I haven't had one since elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.47,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:23.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oho? You wanted to celebrate \Nmy birthday with me that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.54,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,In Russia, leaving someone\Nout of your birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:31.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,sends a clear message that you're done \Nplaying nice with them from that year forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.05,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:38.05,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nothing. I'll spare you \Nfrom any further embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.39,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, buzz off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:44.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Guess we should celebrate it together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:50.15,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Three months late, but I do want us \Nto play nice this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:54.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,There you have it. I'll be throwing \Na belated birthday bash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.66,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Be there or be square.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.25,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:14.96,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Good thing we're not in uniform. \NThose long sleeves are killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.15,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:31.44,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,The president's trying to introduce \Na short-sleeved summer version, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:36.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But even if the proposal goes through, \Nit'll probably be introduced next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:42.44,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wow. People are seriously doing double-takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.00,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, I just noticed that \Nwe're drawing a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:54.50,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Ignore it. It's the price \NI pay for being so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.33,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You probably get hit on a lot \Nwhen you're alone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah. People keep approaching me on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yep, called it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,How do you deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:09.27,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I ramble in Russian until they go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:15.28,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Phew. I was afraid she was fighting them off \Nwith violence—verbal and physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:18.68,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Did you just think \Nsomething very unflattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,'Course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:23.81,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Just glad you're not letting any sleazy \Npick-up artists sweep you off your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:27.48,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, is that a hint of possessiveness? \NActing like my boyfriend now, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.59,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:32.91,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I tend to wanna act like the boyfriend \Nwhen on a date, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.54,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.59,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,A date, huh? Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.43,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}It's my first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:45.18,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess this is your first date {\i0}with me{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:50.87,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I mean, there's no way this hottie has never \Nbeen on a date before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.19,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,164.667)\b1\3c&HDAE2E0&\c&H5B428F&}TGI{\c&H5B4E62&}Beef Steakshack Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.39,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.59,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Dinner here gets pretty pricey,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.95,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,but at lunchtime, you can try a bunch of \Ndifferent meats for a reasonable price.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.25,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Smooth choice, if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:02.67,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.53,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,This place is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:06.71,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I've come here with my family before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.71,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I remember thinking the venison was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.28,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.22,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:21.15,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay, lemme give you a rundown of \Nhow the closing ceremony plays out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:21.97,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:26.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,First, the presidential candidates \Nlay out their motivations and policies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:34.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and then their running mates talk about \Nwhy they're backing him or her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Now, here's the crucial part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:43.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This event doesn't feature any formal\Npolling, but it has something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:43.49,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.57,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,After each pair speaks \Ncomes the audience reaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:50.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and the people in the audience \N{\i1}only{\i0} applaud for the pair they want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:55.76,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Uh, you mean some candidates could be met \Nwith nothing but pin-drop silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.74,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Does that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.84,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:05.30,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking, it's hard to see us \Ngetting a reaction like Yuki will right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.89,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So our goal should be \Nto keep the gap manageable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,No need to try to beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,An awfully passive approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:17.68,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's a realistic assessment \Nof the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:21.05,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Fine, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:24.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Also, we should try to make our speeches first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:28.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,The first pair usually gets a muted response \Nas the crowd weighs up their options.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So we'll have a ready-made excuse \Neven if Yuki shows us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,We do have some other options, \Nbut they'd involve taking the gloves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.47,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:44.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Like playing mind games \Non Yuki and Ayano, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But that wouldn't sit right \Nwith you now, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.56,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It wouldn't, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:52.03,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It'd be a different thing \Nif they tried to start something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:55.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,but I bet even they \Nwouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not like they're Miyamae.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.30,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.62,Default,WAITER,0,0,0,,Here's your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:07.73,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, uh, here's to my birthday, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:08.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:10.92,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.67,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:26.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Were you the one who started \Nthat rumor about Miyamae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.71,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:33.63,flashback,NONOA,0,0,0,,She found out halfway through student congress\N that I had plants in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.80,flashback,NONOA,0,0,0,,Y'know how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:40.28,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nope, that was all her. \NShe even started it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.19,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:46.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That put a stop to \Nall the shit talking about Taniyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,but it also put the outcome \Nof that student congress in limbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry. There might've been \Na better way to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.54,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:01.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I didn't contribute anything. I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.80,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I have no right to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:10.33,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Thanks for doing that for me, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.08,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sure, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:18.02,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What? Is that a blush I see on your cheeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:19.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.08,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.07,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa! She's not even hiding it \Nbehind Russian anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.82,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Here, as a token of my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.83,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Say aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.33,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, look. Somebody's overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:38.33,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She only gets aggressive \Nwhen she thinks I'm flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.09,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Did she forget how she couldn't \Nuse the spoon after the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thanks. That was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:53.85,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wha? She's unfazed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.62,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She's got me right where she wants me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Great meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.50,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.45,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Let me give you your gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:08.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.49,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You actually got me something? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:17.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Talk about a fancy mug! This is really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:22.75,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:26.26,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll put it to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.35,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.74,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:38.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, I just figured cups like this \Nare stuff couples buy in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.77,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Aha, so you do get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.23,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Of course I bought two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.53,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm already using mine at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.03,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:47.78,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What would you think if I said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.16,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.80,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She's really got me figured out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.67,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b1\c&H4D5158&\fs23\frz12.32\frx16\fry334\pos(322.667,115.333)}Student Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.67,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,While we await our turn \Nfor the parent-teacher meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:12.93,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,I'd like to discuss \Nthe summer uniform proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.18,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Okay, let me make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.98,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.94,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Oh, you sit back and relax, Ayano-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.02,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, nah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So, Prez, do you have an update \Non the summer uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.45,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:37.95,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Keep it between us, but I think we can \Nintroduce the new uniforms after summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:44.01,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're going to make a surprise \Nannouncement at the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.84,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,That's wonderful news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:51.47,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,As much as I like this uniform, \Nit gets too hot at this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.91,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.25,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Thanks for saying so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:58.48,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,But Chisaki played the biggest role \Nin getting this proposal approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:02.85,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that. You did this \Nby not letting up in the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.23,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.51,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Toya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:10.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's amazing how easily those two \Ncan enter their own little world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.61,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Okay, tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.66,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thank you, Masha-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.74,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:24.25,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Still bothered by the hypnosis \Nfrom last time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:32.51,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Looks like my parents are here. \NI'll head out for the parent-teacher meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.01,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.75,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,I'll clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.88,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,I'll take you up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.21,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, Masha-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.03,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.03,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I want to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,For the whole hypnosis thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:02.54,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. I started it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.77,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,And, uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.31,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,There's something I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:13.05,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,While I was hypnotized,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.20,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,what did I do to you... exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.05,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You pulled me and Alya into your arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and gave us head pats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.31,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.79,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.15,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:32.06,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm relieved to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.94,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,With that said,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.70,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,did you, uh... see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.99,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun, you perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.71,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry, it was kind of unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.65,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So even Masha-san gets mad about this stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.84,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.59,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She's not the least bit scary. \NIf anything, she's positively adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.03,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.59,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.60,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Are you actually sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whad ar' you 'oing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:02.85,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Punishment for a bad boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:08.25,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Listen, you can't embarrass \Na girl like that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.19,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Okay, that'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:16.79,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like Mom's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.46,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'll handle the rest of the cleanup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.62,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Of course. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:33.41,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Sarashina-senpai and Alya-san are gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:34.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.72,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We're finally alone, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Guess I should go pick up Grandpa, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:42.68,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.75,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Why are you ignoring me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:48.14,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Look who's talking! \NYou're acting like Ayano isn't here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:52.26,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You're being so cold! It's been a while \Nsince we got some sibling time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.91,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I guess it has, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:19:01.62,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I guess you didn't care because \Nyou were off having fun times with Alya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:04.66,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,you... know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.63,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff. I was so wonewy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah? You were wonewy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:12.09,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Be a good girl and get off the desk, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.17,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,So, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.19,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Spoil me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.03,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What is with your mood swings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.83,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What's the holdup? I don't have all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You want it... here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:29.90,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm telling you to spoil me \Nright here and now, Masachika-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:32.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I... understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Come to me, my little kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Never mind! I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.36,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I was just kidding! \NYou were so cool, big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.45,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs7\fade(100,1)\pos(584,235.818)\c&HABABAE&\frz333.7}Grandpa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.08,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, Grandpa's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.30,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:55.21,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Hey, Masachika. There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:57.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What's with the white suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.39,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Don't I look dapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:03.08,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Only peak narcissists and Western mafia \Nwould dress up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:05.95,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.90,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,I forgot to put these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.36,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,There. Aren't I dashing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.73,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}don{\i0}ned those sunglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:15.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay, what movie influenced you this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:17.73,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Actually, why'd you even have this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.75,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,I used my pension to buy it all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Grandma's gonna have a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.84,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Kyotaro too busy to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:30.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, he just got moved to \Nthe Japanese embassy in England this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.37,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,He probably has a lot on his plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.50,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,He could at least make time \Nto meet your teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.35,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,You're such a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.49,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.76,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,We'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.76,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.76,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, Kuze-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.12,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,An Eastern European miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.02,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.88,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Alya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:57.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This is my grandpa, \Nand he's a bit too obsessed with Russia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.90,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh... is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.88,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,May I ask your name, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously, you stop that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Uh... your grandfather seems very spry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.42,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,So, you're Kuze-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's me. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.79,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Would you be Alisa-san's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:16.13,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,My, such a polite young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:20.03,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too. \NI'm Kujo Akemi, Alisa's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.92,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,She's told me lots about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.80,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Good things, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.05,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,Oh, she positively beams \Nwhen talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Does she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.69,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.66,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Would you like to join our family?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:38.69,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, behave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:43.40,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,What do you say to marrying \Nmy boy Masachika here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.02,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Shut your damn mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:51.33,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Is that all right with you, Masachika?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Again, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.04,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:58.50,Default,AKEMI,0,0,0,,Are you going to marry Kuze-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.25,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Quiet, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:05.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,We'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:06.31,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:12.46,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,So, let's talk about this Alisa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:16.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Can we drop that topic... already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:32.08,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:35.25,Default,TOMOHISA,0,0,0,,It's been too long, Yumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:36.83,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,Indeed it has,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.32,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,father-in-law.
